snippet.title: Barbie as The Island Princess Gameplay Nintendo DS
snippet.description:
Barbie as The Island Princess Walkthrough

Let's Play - Barbie as The Island Princess

ABOUT THIS GAME

Barbie as The Island Princess follows the storyline of the popular DVD launch in a fun party-style format.

You'll play as Rosella the shipwrecked princess who is raised by a "family" of animal friends and rescued by Prince Antonio from her tropical island. Through a series of mini-games featuring music and characters from the movie you will venture from Rosella's island home to the Prince's coastal castle in a fun-filled adventure!
